      "writtenOn": "2017-05-15T13:20:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We\u0027ve always heard that this sort of readback from NEON incurs a big delay penalty.  Is that no longer true with ARMv8?  Or is it just that we\u0027re saving enough work to make it worth it?",
